      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEBON STAR (7) goes very well this course and distance starting nine times for three wins and three minors. Below best last time at Murray Bridge (17.54) in a Grade 6, finishing a 6 length fifth. Expected to go close. KIM GOT GAME (1) was well supported last time but could only manage second (20.60), beaten one length. Expected to be in the finish again. LULU DOLL (4) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten 2 lengths, (20.67) at this track. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Expecting another good run. TAZ MANIAC (2) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
